# Source asset dropoffs at the repo root — canonical copies live under
# eval-lab/public/assets/. Keeping the root files out of git prevents
# duplicate-asset confusion and a 600KB+ White.png blob in history.
/White.png
/Comer-industries_placeholder-logo.png

# Raw POV footage — large source videos. The web-friendly transcode that the
# synthetic-pov page actually streams lives at eval-lab/public/assets/ and is
# also kept out of git history (regenerate from source with ffmpeg).
/Phase_8_Video.MP4
*.MP4
eval-lab/public/assets/phase8_pov.mp4
